M|Imme|tx|1. **Freeze hiring** — Don't add sales headcount until payback is fixed
M|Imme|tx|2. **Audit cash runway** — Calculate true runway w/ payment timing
M|Imme|tx|3. **Prioritize existing pipeline** — Close in-flight deals to boost near-term cash
M|Shor|tx|1. **Negotiate annual upfront** — Contact all new prospects, offer 10% discount for annual prepay
M|Shor|2. *|80% of new deals on annual upfront within 90 days**
M|Shor|3. *|Payback drops from 11 months to <2 months**
M|Medi|tx|1. **Shorten sales cycle** — Improve qualification, reduce dead-end deals
M|Medi|2. *|6 months → 4 months sales cycle**
M|Medi|tx|3. **op sales process** — Better demos, faster approvals, streamlined onboarding
M|Long|tx|1. **Validate new payback** — Ensure <6 month payback on annual contracts
M|Long|tx|2. **Gradually scale** — Add sales headcount only when cash payback is proven
M|Long|3. *|1 (invest $1 cash, get $1+ ARR)
